Create card class
create deck class
deck class loads cards
then the deck is given to the character_selector class
the characrter_selector chooses cards in the deck to display

the card class contains a character class
the card is a rect that displays the character rect inside of it
the card can be dragged and dropped
if the card is picked up it turns into the character
if you let go and are colliderect with the character_selector then the card goes back into place (clamp_ip)
while dragging if the character is colliderect with myside then the character is placed at the mouse x and y shifted by half the character size
